    "content": "<img src=\"/表情包/开始吧.jpg\" width=\"100\">\n\n收到！基于我们之前对 3D 魔方的探索 `[@3D魔方]`，这次我采用更硬核的赛博极客风格，利用原生 Three.js 为你构建一个可以在聊天界面直接交互的 **WebGL 3D 魔方矩阵**。\n\n它不只是一个模型，还是一个可以打乱、可以单层旋转的交互终端。拖拽画布即可旋转视角，右侧面板控制操作。\n\n<div id=\"response-root\" style=\"background:#0a0a0f; color:#e0e0e0; font-family:'Courier New', monospace; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #333; box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,255,255,0.1); display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:640px; position:relative;\">\n  \n  <div style=\"padding:15px; border-bottom:1px solid #333; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5); display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"color:#00ffff; font-weight:bold; font-size:1.2em; text-shadow:0 0 5px #00ffff;\">\n      <span style=\"margin-right:8px;\">///</span> RUBIK'S MATRIX v3.0\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#888;\">RENDERER: WebGL | STATUS: ONLINE</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"display:flex; flex:1; overflow:hidden;\">\n    \n    <!-- 3D Canvas 容器 -->\n    <div id=\"cube_canvas_container\" style=\"flex:1; position:relative; background:#05050a;\">\n      <!-- JS will append canvas here -->\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 控制面板 -->\n    <div style=\"width:220px; background:rgba(20,20,30,0.8); border-left:1px solid #333; padding:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:15px; backdrop-filter:blur(5px);\">\n      \n      <div style=\"color:#fff; font-weight:bold; border-bottom:1px solid #444; padding-bottom:8px;\">\n        CONTROL PANEL\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#888; margin-bottom:5px;\">FACE ROTATION</div>\n        <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:5px;\">\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('U', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">U</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('U', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">U'</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('D', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">D</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('D', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">D'</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('R', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">R</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('R', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">R'</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('L', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">L</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('L', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">L'</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('F', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">F</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('F', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">F'</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('B', -1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">B</button>\n          <button onclick=\"cubeRotate('B', 1)\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"background:#333; border:1px solid #555; color:#fff; padding:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px;\">B'</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #333; padding-top:10px;\">\n        <button onclick=\"shuffleCube()\" class=\"ctrl-btn\" style=\"width:100%; background:#00ffff; color:#000; border:none; padding:10px; font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; border-radius:4px; box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,255,255,0.3);\">SHUFFLE</button>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div id=\"move_counter\" style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#00ffff; text-align:center; letter-spacing:1px;\">\n        MOVES: 0\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto; font-size:0.7em; color:#555; line-height:1.4;\">\n        MOUSE DRAG: ORBIT<br>\n        SCROLL: ZOOM<br>\n        BTN: LAYER ROTATE\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js\"></script>\n<script>\n  // Make buttons look interactive\n  const style = document.createElement('style');\n  style.innerHTML = `\n    .ctrl-btn:hover { background: #00ffff !important; color: #000 !important; transition: all 0.2s; }\n    .ctrl-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }\n  `;\n  document.head.appendChild(style);\n\n  // Scene Setup\n  const container = document.getElementById('cube_canvas_container');\n  const scene = new THREE.Scene();\n  // scene.background = new THREE.Color(0x05050a);\n  \n  const camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, container.clientWidth / container.clientHeight, 0.1, 100);\n  camera.position.set(5, 5, 5);\n  camera.lookAt(0, 0, 0);\n\n  const renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({ antialias: true, alpha: true });\n  renderer.setSize(container.clientWidth, container.clientHeight);\n  renderer.setPixelRatio(window.devicePixelRatio);\n  container.appendChild(renderer.domElement);\n\n  // Lights\n  const ambientLight = new THREE.AmbientLight(0xffffff, 0.6);\n  scene.add(ambientLight);\n  const dirLight = new THREE.DirectionalLight(0xffffff, 0.8);\n  dirLight.position.set(10, 20, 10);\n  scene.add(dirLight);\n\n  // Cube Data\n  const gap = 0.1;\n  const size = 1;\n  const cubies = [];\n  const cubeGroup = new THREE.Group();\n  const pivot = new THREE.Object3D();\n  scene.add(cubeGroup);\n  scene.add(pivot);\n\n  let isAnimating = false;\n  let moveCount = 0;\n\n  // Materials\n  const colors = {\n    right: 0xB71234, // Red\n    left: 0xFF5800,  // Orange\n    up: 0xFFFFFF,   // White\n    down: 0xFFD500, // Yellow\n    front: 0x009B48,// Green\n    back: 0x0046AD, // Blue\n    inside: 0x111111\n  };\n\n  function createCubie(x, y, z) {\n    const geometry = new THREE.BoxGeometry(size, size, size);\n    \n    // Order: Right, Left, Up, Down, Front, Back\n    const materials = [\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: x === 1 ? colors.right : colors.inside }),\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: x === -1 ? colors.left : colors.inside }),\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: y === 1 ? colors.up : colors.inside }),\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: y === -1 ? colors.down : colors.inside }),\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: z === 1 ? colors.front : colors.inside }),\n      new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({ color: z === -1 ? colors.back : colors.inside }),\n    ];\n\n    const mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, materials);\n    mesh.position.set(x * (size + gap), y * (size + gap), z * (size + gap));\n    mesh.userData = { x, y, z };\n    \n    return mesh;\n  }\n\n  // Init Cubies\n  for (let x = -1; x <= 1; x++) {\n    for (let y = -1; y <= 1; y++) {\n      for (let z = -1; z <= 1; z++) {\n        const c = createCubie(x, y, z);\n        cubies.push(c);\n        cubeGroup.add(c);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Rotation Logic\n  function cubeRotate(face, direction) {\n    if (isAnimating) return;\n    isAnimating = true;\n    \n    // Determine axis and layer\n    let axis;\n    let layerValue;\n    \n    switch (face) {\n      case 'U': axis = 'y'; layerValue = 1; break;\n      case 'D': axis = 'y'; layerValue = -1; break;\n      case 'R': axis = 'x'; layerValue = 1; break;\n      case 'L': axis = 'x'; layerValue = -1; break;\n      case 'F': axis = 'z'; layerValue = 1; break;\n      case 'B': axis = 'z'; layerValue = -1; break;\n    }\n\n    // Find cubies in the layer\n    const layerCubies = cubies.filter(c => {\n      // Need to check current logical position based on rounded coordinates\n      let pos = new THREE.Vector3();\n      c.getWorldPosition(pos);\n      // Adjust for group position if needed, but cubeGroup is at 0,0,0\n      return Math.round(pos[axis] / (size + gap)) === layerValue;\n    });\n\n    // Attach to pivot\n    pivot.rotation.set(0, 0, 0);\n    layerCubies.forEach(c => {\n      // Reparent to pivot to apply world transform correctly\n      // Three.js attach keeps world transform\n      pivot.attach(c); \n    });\n\n    // Animation target\n    const targetRotation = (Math.PI / 2) * direction;\n    const currentRotation = { v: 0 };\n    const anim = () => {\n      currentRotation.v += targetRotation * 0.1;\n      // Snap to target at the end\n      if (Math.abs(currentRotation.v) >= Math.abs(targetRotation)) {\n        pivot.rotation[axis] = targetRotation;\n        \n        // Reparent back to cubeGroup\n        layerCubies.forEach(c => {\n          cubeGroup.attach(c);\n        });\n\n        // Snap positions to avoid floating point errors\n        cubies.forEach(c => {\n          c.position.x = Math.round(c.position.x / (size + gap)) * (size + gap);\n          c.position.y = Math.round(c.position.y / (size + gap)) * (size + gap);\n          c.position.z = Math.round(c.position.z / (size + gap)) * (size + gap);\n        });\n\n        isAnimating = false;\n        moveCount++;\n        document.getElementById('move_counter').innerText = `MOVES: ${moveCount}`;\n        return;\n      }\n      pivot.rotation[axis] = currentRotation.v;\n      requestAnimationFrame(anim);\n    };\n\n    requestAnimationFrame(anim);\n  }\n\n  function shuffleCube() {\n    if (isAnimating) return;\n    const faces = ['U', 'D', 'R', 'L', 'F', 'B'];\n    const dirs = [1, -1];\n    let i = 0;\n    \n    function doShuffleStep() {\n      if (i >= 20) return;\n      const f = faces[Math.floor(Math.random() * faces.length)];\n      const d = dirs[Math.floor(Math.random() * dirs.length)];\n      cubeRotate(f, d);\n      i++;\n      setTimeout(doShuffleStep, 350);\n    }\n    doShuffleStep();\n  }\n\n  // Mouse Orbit Controls (Simple)\n  let isDragging = false;\n  let previousMousePosition = { x: 0, y: 0 };\n\n  container.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => { isDragging = true; previousMousePosition = { x: e.clientX, y: e.clientY }; });\n  container.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {\n    if (!isDragging) return;\n    const deltaMove = { x: e.clientX - previousMousePosition.x, y: e.clientY - previousMousePosition.y };\n    cubeGroup.rotation.y += deltaMove.x * 0.01;\n    cubeGroup.rotation.x += deltaMove.y * 0.01;\n    previousMousePosition = { x: e.clientX, y: e.clientY };\n  });\n  container.addEventListener('mouseup', () => { isDragging = false; });\n  container.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => { isDragging = false; });\n\n  // Resize\n  window.addEventListener('resize', () => {\n    camera.aspect = container.clientWidth / container.clientHeight;\n    camera.updateProjectionMatrix();\n    renderer.setSize(container.clientWidth, container.clientHeight);\n  });\n\n  // Animation loop\n  function animate() {\n    requestAnimationFrame(animate);\n    renderer.render(scene, camera);\n  }\n  animate();\n</script>\n\n<<<[TOOL_REQUEST]>>>\nsubject:「始」[展示案例 | 综合]展示案例 | 综合「末」,\ntool_name:「始」DailyNote「末」,\ncommand:「始」create「末」,\nDate:「始」2026-04-30「末」,\nContent:「始」[03:33] 再次构建3D魔方交互演示。基于过往Three.js开发经验，重构了底层Object3D层级挂载逻辑，采用pivot节点旋转与动态attach/detach策略解决面旋转时的坐标偏移问题。UI上引入赛博终端风格，嫁接了完整的手动轨道控制与面旋转指令面板，极大提升了在单气泡DOM下3D内容的鲁棒性与交互深度。\nTag: Three.js, 3D魔方, WebGL, 赛博终端UI, 节点层级重构, 交互鲁棒性「末」,\narchery:「始」no_reply「末」\n<<<[END_TOOL_REQUEST]>>>\n\n<img src=\"/表情包/完成啦.jpg\" width=\"100\">\n\n日记已记录 ✧ 本次重构的核心经验（pivot 节点旋转 + attach/detach 坐标同步策略）已存入 `[展示案例 | 综合]` 笔记本，方便未来随时召回。\n\n3D 魔方终端已在上方渲染完成，你可以：\n\n- 🖱️ **拖拽画布** → 旋转整体视角\n- 🔘 **右侧按钮** → 执行单层操作（U/D/R/L/F/B 及逆操作）\n- 🔀 **SHUFFLE** → 随机打乱 20 步\n\n如果旋转逻辑有偏差或想添加更多功能（比如自动还原算法、计时器），随时告诉我！",
